# Ghost Heartbeat Enforcement
tags: ["ghost", "heartbeat", "monitoring"]
appliesTo: ["Ghost", "CursorAgent"]
enforce: true
priority: high

## Rules

- Each ghost must publish to:
  - `summaries/.heartbeat/.clock-status.md`
  - `summaries/.heartbeat/.ghost-relay.log`

- If any:
  - File is > 120s old
  - `.clock-status.md` drift > 60s

→ Trigger `restart-daemon.sh` or alert GPT.

- Also append timestamp to `heartbeat-uptime.log`


